Package examples

Class Summary
id3d Reads a V2 tag from a file and opens a window to edit all V2 frames encountered.
id3d2 Reads a V2 tag from a file and opens a window to edit all V2 frames encountered.
id3d3 Reads a V1 tag from a file, copies the contents into a V2 tag and writes this back to the file.
id3d4 Reads a whole directory and writes all information it encounters to a file
id3d5 Just maximum debug
